title: Apple’s Siri confused between Dussehra and Eid
text:
Apple’s Siri confused between Dussehra and Eid 
Times Of India Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
Upon being asked "Is it a holiday today?" the voice assistant answers that it is Dussehra, and then wishing them "Eid Mubarak."...
